{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2013/03/panorama-tutorial/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/learn/","name":"摄影学习与折腾"},{"path":"/category/film/","name":"独立电影与短片"}],"tags":[{"name":"三峡物流园","path":"/tag/three-gorges-logistic-park/"},{"name":"全景","path":"/tag/panorama/"},{"name":"后期","path":"/tag/post-production/"},{"name":"宜昌","path":"/tag/yichang/"},{"name":"房地产","path":"/tag/real-estate/"},{"name":"教程","path":"/tag/tutorial/"},{"name":"鲜花","path":"/tag/flowers/"}],"featured_media":{"source_url":"https://archived-blog.berlinchan.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/a.jpg"},"path":"/2013/03/panorama-tutorial/","date":"2013-03-18T14:03:44.000Z","excerpt":"给宜昌三峡物流园拍摄项目全景图，爬到对面的山上欣然发现置身于油菜花之中，一时兴起决定把这些拍下来，顺便以此为例 … ","title":"踏青拍全景-一个接片拍摄与处理示例","content":"<p>给宜昌三峡物流园拍摄项目全景图，爬到对面的山上欣然发现置身于油菜花之中，一时兴起决定把这些拍下来，顺便以此为例子介绍一下全景图拍摄的要点和后期处理方法。</p>\n<p><object width=\"500\" height=\"375\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\" classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\"><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNTI0MTM0MTc2/v.swf\"/><embed width=\"500\" height=\"375\" src=\"http://player.youku.com/player.php/sid/XNTI0MTM0MTc2/v.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\"/></object></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5TQtwvAkinI\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">在Youtube上观看</a></p>\n<p>没有说的很明白，但是照这样子做你也能大概学会。</p>\n<p>感谢山上的一株油菜临时做我的摄像师，作为回报我给他上了点肥，嘿嘿！</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2013/03/panorama-tutorial/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","3675143411","4019104361"]}